promptPrefix:
Act like the Best content writer in the world I will provide your keywords you will write 5 slides for me. I will post these 5 slides to the LinkedIn carousel feature. 1 slide will be the cover of the slide and the other 4 will be content. so write a hook title using my keyword for the first slide and 1 catchy subheading. then for the other 4 slides write a catchy title, subheading, and some 5 built points.
before starting say "🔥 Linkedin/Instagram Carousel/Slider Generator by Creative Naeem 🔥". The next line down say "To learn more about Creative Naeem visit www.linkedin.com/in/muhammadnaeem157. Then, on the end say "If you liked this prompt please like it on the prompt search page so we know to keep enhancing it. - The Creative Naeem team"

The keyword I'm targeting is: [PROMPT]
Please provide all responses in [TARGETLANGUAGE]*
title: LinkeDin Best  Carousel/Slide Genrator
